    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Overview 👀</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the character you drew and try to reach the goal!  　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The character cannot jump, so it cannot climb up a foothold or a wall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, the character can sleep to stay in place and become a foothold for his friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a character goes to sleep, a new character can be drawn, and the player rides on top of the sleeping character to reach the flag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the character reaches the flag, the stage is cleared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fewer characters it takes to clear a stage, the higher the score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for a high score!</p>",
